&lt;p align=&#34;left&#34; style=&#34;font-size:16px&#34;&gt;
DrugBank ID: &lt;a href=&#39;https://www.drugbank.ca/drugs/db12418&#39; target=&#39;_blank&#39;&gt;db12418&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt;
